{"tid":1878981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】屯院宿舍供醫護自我隔離　水龍頭湧臭味黑色污水　傢俱覆滿塵垢","createTime":"2020-02-14T02:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T03:49:02.000Z","uid":251328,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4683e4ed47c06766dea2fdc17d8cb93331f2ad96","tid":1878981,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"屯門醫院多年來有「地獄醫院」之稱，惟其護士宿舍亦仿如地獄。近日不少醫護人員因擔心接觸新型冠狀病毒確診患者後會傳染家人，決定到院方提供的護士宿舍自我隔離，發現情況相當恐怖。《立場新聞》獲得多張相片，顯示屯門醫院的護士宿舍衛生情況極惡劣，醫護指，廁所水龍頭持續10分鐘湧出惡臭黑色污水，另外床褥、枱面、地氈等有大量塵垢污跡，估計長時間沒有人清潔。屯門醫院發言人回覆《立場新聞》查詢指，院方對臨時員工宿舍的狀況欠佳深感抱歉，即時聯絡同事更換房間，又承諾今後會加強監察宿位的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnRroVC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnRroVC.jpg&h=5f922384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/r-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%AF%E9%99%A2%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E4%BE%9B%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E8%87%AA%E6%88%91%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-%E6%B0%B4%E9%BE%8D%E9%A0%AD%E6%B9%A7%E9%BB%91%E8%89%B2%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4-%E5%90%84%E6%A8%A3%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%B1%E9%81%8D%E4%BD%88%E7%81%B0%E5%A1%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fr-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E4%25BE%259B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E5%2582%25A2%25E4%25BF%25B1%25E9%2581%258D%25E4%25BD%2588%25E7%2581%25B0%25E5%25A1%25B5%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=34347beb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fr-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E4%25BE%259B%25E9%25